'''格莱美传奇奖'''（{{lang-en|'''Grammy Legend Award''' 或称 '''Grammy Living Legend Award'''}}）<ref name="Liza: Life in the limelight">{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/4506978/|title=Liza: Life in the limelight|last=Kotb|first=Hoda|date=2004-03-12|publisher=[[msnbc.com|msnbc.com]]|accessdate=2009-12-31|archive-date=2012-12-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6D0eJqi0R?url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/4506978/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Billy Joel biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/music/artist/joel_billy/artist.jhtml|title=Billy Joel biography|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|accessdate=2009-12-31|archive-date=2009-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091227085849/http://www.mtv.com/music/artist/joel_billy/artist.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]中为表彰“在唱片领域做出杰出贡献和影响的人士”所设立的一项特别荣誉奖。<ref name="Grammy Legend Award" />格莱美奖最初称为“留声机奖”（Gramophone Awards），<ref name="Seen and heard at the 50th Grammy Awards">{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/2008-02-10-3988122778_x.htm|title=Seen and heard at the 50th Grammy Awards|date=2008-02-11|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|publisher=Gannett Company|accessdate=2009-12-20|archive-date=2020-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530091646/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/2008-02-10-3988122778_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The 2001 Grammys">{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2001/feb/18/entertainment/ca-26779|title=The 2001 Grammys|last=Henken|first=John|date=2001-02-18|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|format=访问全文需要付费|accessdate=2009-12-20|publisher=Tribune Company|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105155738/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/feb/18/entertainment/ca-26779|dead-url=no}}</ref>由美国国家录音艺术与科学学院负责评选。首届格莱美奖于1959年颁发，之后每年举行一次颁奖仪式。格莱美奖涵盖多个音乐领域，所表彰的对象是对[[音乐产业|音乐产业]]有着杰出成就的人士。<ref name="Top Grammy Winners Announced">{{cite web|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/599116022.html?dids=599116022:599116022&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Mar+13%2C+1970&author=&pub=Los+Angeles+Times&desc=Top+Grammy+Winners+Announced&pqatl=google|title=Top Grammy Winners Announced|last=Hilburn|first=Richard|date=1970-03-13|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Tribune Company|format=访问全文需要付费|accessdate=2009-12-20|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024102452/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/599116022.html?dids=599116022:599116022&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Mar+13,+1970&author=&pub=Los+Angeles+Times&desc=Top+Grammy+Winners+Announced&pqatl=google|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="The Prem Rawat Foundation Presents Its Initiatives at the Grammy Awards">{{cite web|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-29606295_ITM|title=The Prem Rawat Foundation Presents Its Initiatives at the Grammy Awards|date=2007-02-09|publisher=America's Intelligence Wire|format=访问全文需要订阅|accessdate=2009-12-21|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021092452/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-29606295_ITM|dead-url=no}}</ref>

格莱美传奇奖于1990年首次颁发给了[[安德鲁·劳埃德·韦伯|安德鲁·劳埃德·韦伯]]、[[丽莎·明尼利|丽莎·明尼利]]、[[史摩基·羅賓森|史摩基·羅賓森]]和{{le|威利·纳尔逊|Willie Nelson}}四位音乐家。次年，另外四位音乐家（[[艾瑞莎·弗兰克林|艾瑞莎·弗兰克林]]、[[比利·乔尔|比利·乔尔]]、[[约翰尼·卡什|约翰尼·卡什]]和[[昆西·琼斯|昆西·琼斯]]）获此殊荣。[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]和[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]分别于1992年和1993年获得此奖项。

1994年，美国的两位音乐家[[柯提斯·梅菲爾德|柯提斯·梅菲爾德]]和[[弗兰克·西纳特拉|弗兰克·西纳特拉]]获得了格莱美传奇奖。在此之后，奖项不再每年进行颁发。1998年，意大利[[歌剧|歌剧]][[男高音|男高音]]歌唱家[[卢奇亚诺·帕瓦罗蒂|卢奇亚诺·帕瓦罗蒂]]获奖。羿年，奖项颁发给了英国的创作歌手[[艾尔顿·约翰|艾尔顿·约翰]]。2003年，英国三人兄弟乐队组合[[比吉斯|比吉斯]]成为21世纪以来首位获奖者。截至目前，共有14位音乐家和一个乐队获得了该奖项。

